T1  - Does exposure to foreign competition affect stock liquidity? Evidence from industry-level import data
AU  - Atawnah, Nader
AU  - Balachandran, Balasingham
AU  - Duong, Huu Nhan
AU  - Podolski, Edward J.
JO  - Journal of Financial Markets
VL  - 39
